{"name":"Focus Fire (Ex; 2nd, Fighting Style)","permission":{"default":0,"hg1bBCAUsIDPKim6":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>&gt;@Item[j60rojbL3unRF31n]{Sharpshoot}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">When you make a full attack with a ranged weapon, you can make both attacks with a &ndash;3 penalty instead of a &ndash;4 penalty as long as they both target the same creature. If your first attack kills or knocks out the target, you can instead make the second attack against a different creature at a &ndash;4 penalty. Once you have the soldier&rsquo;s onslaught class feature (see page 112), you can use this ability with it, making three attacks against the same creature at a &ndash;5 penalty; if your first or second attack kills or knocks out your target, you can make your remaining attacks against a different creature at a &ndash;6 penalty.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Sharpshoot","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":null,"per":""},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"2nd Bonus","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"exportSource":{"world":"practice-starfinder","system":"sfrpg","coreVersion":"0.6.5","systemVersion":"0.3.3"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"nhDmOHBfDT9CrP62"}
{"name":"Grenade Expert (Ex; 1st, Fighting Style)","permission":{"default":0,"hg1bBCAUsIDPKim6":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>&gt;<span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">@Item[FkuDc522TWw3WGHE]{Bombard}</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">You increase the range increment of your thrown grenades by 5 Ã— your Strength bonus. In addition, youâ€™re able to salvage enough materials to create a grenade without paying for it. Creating a grenade takes 10 minutes. You can create any grenade whose item level is less than or equal to your soldier level, but this grenade is unstable and only you can use it effectively. If anyone else tries to use the grenade, it is a dud. You can have only one grenade created by this ability at one time (if you create a new grenade using this ability, the old grenade no longer works).</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Bombard","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":null,"per":""},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"1st Bonus","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"exportSource":{"world":"practice-starfinder","system":"sfrpg","coreVersion":"0.6.5","systemVersion":"0.3.3"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"o3of4ZOcQh73v2PL"}
{"name":"Flash Freeze (Ex; 7th Level)","permission":{"default":0,"hg1bBCAUsIDPKim6":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">&gt;@Item[wFTC0sGqdpnZUib4]{Gear Boost}</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl03_LabelName\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl11_LabelName\">When you hit a creature with a weapon in the cryo category, that creature&rsquo;s speeds are reduced by 10 feet for 1 round, to a minimum of 10 feet.</span><br /></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Gear Boost","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"7th Level","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"exportSource":{"world":"practice-starfinder","system":"sfrpg","coreVersion":"0.6.5","systemVersion":"0.3.3"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"oVHanBDOmRCHjOop"}
{"name":"Secret of the Magi (Su; 2nd, Fighting Style)","permission":{"default":0,"hg1bBCAUsIDPKim6":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>&gt;@Item[33fxlqpShtqndjry]{Arcane Assailant}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">When you imbue a weapon with the rune of the eldritch knight, in addition to its normal benefits, the rune grants the weapon one of the following weapon fusions of your choice: <em>ethereal</em>, <em>flaming</em>, <em>frost</em>, <em>merciful</em>, or <em>shock</em>. The weapon can&rsquo;t gain a fusion it already has, and this bonus fusion doesn&rsquo;t count toward the maximum total level of fusions the weapon can have at once. The bonus fusion ends when the weapon ceases to be imbued with the rune of the eldritch knight. For more information on fusions, see page 191.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Arcane Assailant","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"2nd Bonus","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"exportSource":{"world":"practice-starfinder","system":"sfrpg","coreVersion":"0.6.5","systemVersion":"0.3.3"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"pmfUCwbfro8X8F3s"}
{"name":"Plasma Immolation (Ex; 7th Level)","permission":{"default":0,"hg1bBCAUsIDPKim6":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">&gt;@Item[wFTC0sGqdpnZUib4]{Gear Boost}</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl03_LabelName\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl17_LabelName\">You are expert at setting things on fire with plasma. If your attack roll with a weapon in the plasma category is a 19 (the d20 shows a 19), and the attack hits your target, the target gains the burning condition. The condition deals 1d4 fire damage if the weapon has an item level of 1st-6th, 1d8 if its item level is 7th-14th, and 2d8 if its item level is 15th or higher.</span><br></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Gear Boost","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"7th Level","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"exportSource":{"world":"practice-starfinder","system":"sfrpg","coreVersion":"0.6.5","systemVersion":"0.3.3"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"vTj7MQPHUvhnhcj4"}
{"name":"Heavy Onslaught (Ex; 11th Level)","permission":{"default":0,"hg1bBCAUsIDPKim6":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">&gt;@Item[wFTC0sGqdpnZUib4]{Gear Boost}</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl03_LabelName\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl12_LabelName\">Your attacks with heavy weapons bypass part of the targetâ€™s damage reduction. If your heavy weapon does not already overcome the targetâ€™s damage reduction, treat the targetâ€™s damage reduction as though it were 5 lower. At 15th level, treat the targetâ€™s damage reduction as 10 lower.</span><br></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Gear Boost","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"11th Level","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"exportSource":{"world":"practice-starfinder","system":"sfrpg","coreVersion":"0.6.5","systemVersion":"0.3.3"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"wRByX3EfIFGU3PQw"}
{"name":"Sniper's Aim (Ex; 1st, Fighting Style)","permission":{"default":0,"hg1bBCAUsIDPKim6":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>&gt;@Item[j60rojbL3unRF31n]{Sharpshoot}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">When you make a ranged attack against a target with cover, reduce the AC bonus from cover by 2. You canâ€™t use sniperâ€™s aim against an enemy with total cover.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Sharpshoot","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":null,"per":""},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"1st Bonus","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"exportSource":{"world":"practice-starfinder","system":"sfrpg","coreVersion":"0.6.5","systemVersion":"0.3.3"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"xFf9jGFwjUO2n47F"}
{"name":"Perfect Opportunity (Ex; 4th, Fighting Style)","permission":{"default":0,"hg1bBCAUsIDPKim6":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>&gt;<a class=\"entity-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-entity=\"Item\" data-id=\"cR8wnyEBfjeelFdA\"> Blitz</a></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">When you hit a creature with an attack of opportunity, that creature canâ€™t move out of the squares you threaten until the start of its next turn. In addition, when an enemy takes a guarded step (see page 247) out of a square you threaten, you can make an attack of opportunity against it with a â€“2 penalty to the attack roll. If the target provoked an attack of opportunity by moving, hitting with your attack of opportunity ends the targetâ€™s movement immediately, preventing it from carrying out the rest of its movement.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Blitz","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":null,"per":""},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"4th Bonus","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"exportSource":{"world":"practice-starfinder","system":"sfrpg","coreVersion":"0.6.5","systemVersion":"0.3.3"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"zhOsc5OFVaW7az9D"}
